  Fixup docs and examples installation, bug 472908.

  28 May 2013; Mike Gilbert <floppym@gentoo.org>
  +files/imaging-1.1.7-no-xv.patch,
  +files/pillow-2.0.0-delete_hardcoded_paths.patch,
